summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5511 for the construction of a trunk sewer to be known as Laurelhurst Trunk Sewer Unit \#2, in an easement across private property, along the shore of Lake Washington from East 43rd Street to Ambleside, (an undedicated street in the unrecorded plat of Windermere), under Ordinance No. 70511, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
